      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Ready for a reliable companion that\u2019s seen some adventures? This car is in fair condition and is perfect for someone looking for a solid, functional vehicle at a great price! It carries some honest signs of use and character from its time on the road, but it\u2019s still got plenty of life left and is eager for its next journey. If you value practicality and a proven track record, this is the ride for you!",
