    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for this awesome ride. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape, totally ready for all your upcoming road trips! It drives like a dream and has been well-loved and maintained over the years. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great and feels even better behind the wheel, this is the one. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you're going to love it!",
