    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS. This example boasts a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and an M-Variable limited-slip differential for pure mechanical engagement. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized: the rear subframe has been reinforced to mitigate floor pan stress, and the rod bearings have been replaced. The suspension features refreshed bushings and Koni dampers, ensuring the chassis remains communicative and taut. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain is robust and the steering rack is precise, making this an ideal candidate for the spirited enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
