      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and presents beautifully in its original factory finish. The exterior retains a deep gloss with only the minor, expected road wear consistent with careful, long-term ownership. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery is supple and free of tears, and every feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity sound system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust and dependable, having undergone regular scheduled servicing to ensure a smooth, responsive drive. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the engine bay is remarkably clean, reflecting the pride of ownership this car has enjoyed. It is a complete, turn-key package for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-performing vehicle that looks as impressive as it handles.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
